---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/inner.css';
---

<BaseLayout locale="en" localizedPaths={{ pt: '/opera-os', en: '/en/opera-os', es: '/es/opera-os' }}
  title="OperaOS: Complete AI implementation in 10-12 weeks · Catalise.me"
  description="OPERA OS is the intelligence installed at the core of your business. In 10 to 12 weeks: AI agents handling customer service 24/7, an organized CRM, connected departments, a real-time dashboard, and a trained team."
  ogTitle="Opera OS: AI operating system · Catalise.me"
  ogDescription="OPERA Method in 5 phases, 10-12 weeks. Investment proportional to operation. CRM, AI agents, automations, and training." ogUrl="https://catalise.me/en/opera-os" canonical="https://catalise.me/en/opera-os"
  bodyClass="page-opera"
  pageType="inner"
>

    <!-- HERO -->
    <header class="page-hero" aria-labelledby="opera-hero-heading">
      <video class="page-hero-video-bg" data-src="/assets/system.mp4" loop muted playsinline preload="none" aria-hidden="true"></video>
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow hero-animate-1">Main Product</p>
        <h1 id="opera-hero-heading" class="page-hero-title hero-animate-2">
          OPERA OS <em>is the intelligence installed at the core of your business.</em>
        </h1>

        <div class="hero-pills hero-animate-4">
          <div class="hero-pill">
            <span class="hero-pill-label">Timeline</span>
            <span class="hero-pill-value">10 to 12 weeks</span>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-pill">
            <span class="hero-pill-label">Investment</span>
            <span class="hero-pill-value">Defined in the diagnosis</span>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-pill">
            <span class="hero-pill-label">Includes</span>
            <span class="hero-pill-value">CRM + AI + Website + Automations + Training</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-ctas hero-animate-4" style="margin-top: 40px;">
          <a href="/en/contato" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" id="opera-hero-cta">
            I want my free diagnosis <span class="btn-arrow">→</span>
          </a>
          <a href="#metodo" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">
            See the OPERA method
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- OS 5 SINTOMAS -->
    <section id="sintomas" aria-labelledby="sintomas-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header reveal">
          <p class="eyebrow">The Diagnosis</p>
          <h2 id="sintomas-heading">Your business <em>works</em>.<br> But it does not <em>operate with central intelligence</em>.</h2>
          <p>There is a huge difference between a business that survives on daily effort and a business that runs guided by intelligent systems. The first depends on you for everything. The second operates while your team handles what matters most.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="symptom-grid reveal">
          <div class="symptom-card">
            <span class="symptom-number">01</span>
            <div class="symptom-content">
              <h3>Manual and reactive operation</h3>
              <p>Processes that rely on memory, spreadsheets, or the owner's physical presence. Average: <strong>286 hours/year lost</strong>.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="symptom-card">
            <span class="symptom-number">02</span>
            <div class="symptom-content">
              <h3>Leads that disappear without response</h3>
              <p>Opportunities arrive outside business hours and go to competitors. <strong>Conversion drops 80% after 15 minutes</strong>.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="symptom-card">
            <span class="symptom-number">03</span>
            <div class="symptom-content">
              <h3>Decisions without data</h3>
              <p>Managers make pricing, marketing, and team decisions based on intuition. <strong>67% of managers</strong> do not have updated data.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="symptom-card">
            <span class="symptom-number">04</span>
            <div class="symptom-content">
              <h3>Growth increases chaos</h3>
              <p>More clients, more problems. More revenue, more staff. The business scales work, not results.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="symptom-card">
            <span class="symptom-number">05</span>
            <div class="symptom-content">
              <h3>Owner hostage to their own business</h3>
              <p>Started for freedom. Became the central system of everything. Checkout at noon. The mind never stops.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- O QUE É / WE ARE É -->
    <section id="o-que-e" aria-labelledby="o-que-e-heading">
      <div class="container container-sm">
        <div class="section-header reveal">
          <p class="eyebrow">The Product</p>
          <h2 id="o-que-e-heading">OPERA OS is the method that <em>transforms how your business operates.</em></h2>
        </div>

        <div class="prose reveal">
          <p>It’s not software you subscribe to and configure alone. It’s the end-to-end implementation of the AI operating system in your business.</p>
          <p>What we deliver is an integrated ecosystem: the agent answering on WhatsApp feeds the CRM, which guides sales, which reports on the dashboard, which informs management decisions. All connected, all recorded, all evolving.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="nao-NOT reveal" style="margin-top: 40px;">
          <h3 style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: var(--text-muted);">What <strong style="color: var(--text-primary);">WE ARE</strong> NOT</h3>
          <div class="nao-NOT-list">
            <div class="nao-NOT-item">❌ Marketing agency that delivers campaigns and leaves</div>
            <div class="nao-NOT-item">❌ Consultancy that delivers reports for you to implement alone</div>
            <div class="nao-NOT-item">❌ Isolated software that solves one problem and creates three more</div>
          </div>
          <div class="NOT-item">
            ✅ <strong>The AI operating system of your business: built, integrated, and running</strong>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- MÉTODO OPERA DETALHADO -->
    <section id="metodo" aria-labelledby="metodo-heading">
      <div class="container container-sm">
        <div class="section-header reveal">
          <p class="eyebrow">The OPERA Method</p>
          <h2 id="metodo-heading">The five phases, <em>one by one</em>.</h2>
          <p>Every implementation follows the method in 5 phases: you follow the sequence of each step in the process.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="opera-timeline">
          <div class="opera-phase reveal">
            <div class="opera-phase-header">
              <span class="opera-phase-letter">O</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="opera-phase-title">Organization</h3>
                <span class="opera-phase-weeks text-mono">Weeks 1–2</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="opera-phase-body">
              <p>In-depth diagnosis. We map every process, from first contact to after-sales, and classify bottlenecks by real financial impact. <strong>Delivery: prioritized bottleneck report.</strong></p>
              <div class="deliverable">
                <span class="deliverable-label">Deliverable</span>
                Executive report with each bottleneck mapped, classified by estimated cost impact.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="opera-phase reveal">
            <div class="opera-phase-header">
              <span class="opera-phase-letter">P</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="opera-phase-title">Planning</h3>
                <span class="opera-phase-weeks text-mono">Weeks 2–3</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="opera-phase-body">
              <p>We define scope, implementation order, and projected ROI per initiative. <strong>Delivery: master plan with goals, timeline, and finalized investment.</strong></p>
              <div class="deliverable">
                <span class="deliverable-label">Deliverable</span>
                Master document with finalized scope, timeline, projected KPIs, and expected ROI per initiative.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="opera-phase reveal">
            <div class="opera-phase-header">
              <span class="opera-phase-letter">E</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="opera-phase-title">Strategy</h3>
                <span class="opera-phase-weeks text-mono">Weeks 3–4</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="opera-phase-body">
              <p>Technical architecture: which agents, which integrations, how everything connects, and the team adoption plan. <strong>Delivery: complete blueprint.</strong></p>
              <div class="deliverable">
                <span class="deliverable-label">Deliverable</span>
                Complete visual and technical blueprint: flows, integrations, responsibilities, and implementation sequence.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="opera-phase reveal">
            <div class="opera-phase-header">
              <span class="opera-phase-letter">R</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="opera-phase-title">Execution</h3>
                <span class="opera-phase-weeks text-mono">Weeks 4–8</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="opera-phase-body">
              <p>Building and activation. We integrate systems, deploy agents, and train the team. <strong>Delivery: functioning system.</strong></p>
              <div class="deliverable">
                <span class="deliverable-label">Deliverable</span>
                System running, team trained, complete operational documentation.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="opera-phase reveal">
            <div class="opera-phase-header">
              <span class="opera-phase-letter">A</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="opera-phase-title">Tuning</h3>
                <span class="opera-phase-weeks text-mono">Weeks 8–10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="opera-phase-body">
              <p>Calibration with real data from the first 30 days. We adjust agents to your specific business. <strong>Delivery: certified system.</strong></p>
              <div class="deliverable">
                <span class="deliverable-label">Deliverable</span>
                Final validation and delivery of the certified system.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- O QUE ESTÁ INCLUÍDO -->
    <section id="inclui" aria-labelledby="inclui-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header reveal" style="text-align:center; align-items:center;">
          <p class="eyebrow" style="justify-content:center;">The Scope</p>
          <h2 id="inclui-heading">Everything your company needs to <em>operate</em>.</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0 auto;">The final scope is defined in Phase O. But Opera OS always delivers the complete ecosystem.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="includes-grid reveal">
          <div class="include-item">
            <span class="include-icon"><i data-lucide="globe" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
            <h3>Digital presence</h3>
            <p>Website, blog, optimized sales pages</p>
          </div>
          <div class="include-item">
            <span class="include-icon"><i data-lucide="layout-grid" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
            <h3>AI agent</h3>
            <p>24/7 support trained on your business</p>
          </div>
          <div class="include-item">
            <span class="include-icon"><i data-lucide="monitor" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
            <h3>Authentic CRM</h3>
            <p>Commercial Kanban, funnel, dashboard</p>
          </div>
          <div class="include-item">
            <span class="include-icon"><i data-lucide="pen-tool" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
            <h3>Orchestrated automations</h3>
            <p>Complete automated customer journey</p>
          </div>
          <div class="include-item">
            <span class="include-icon"><i data-lucide="message-square" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
            <h3>Support stack</h3>
            <p>Integrated and configured support hub</p>
          </div>
          <div class="include-item">
            <span class="include-icon"><i data-lucide="activity" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
            <h3>Sales funnel</h3>
            <p>Complete capture and conversion structure</p>
          </div>
          <div class="include-item">
            <span class="include-icon"><i data-lucide="bar-chart-3" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
            <h3>Channel strategy</h3>
            <p>Direct vs optimized intermediaries</p>
          </div>
          <div class="include-item">
            <span class="include-icon"><i data-lucide="users" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
            <h3>Team training</h3>
            <p>Complete onboarding and documentation</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PARA QUEM / WE ARE É -->
    <section id="qualificacao" aria-labelledby="qual-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header reveal">
          <p class="eyebrow">Qualification</p>
          <h2 id="qual-heading">Opera OS <em>is for you</em> if...</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="qual-grid reveal">
          <div class="qual-col yes">
            <div class="qual-header"><span class="qual-badge">It’s for you</span></div>
            <ul class="qual-list">
              <li>
                <span class="qual-icon"><i data-lucide="check" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
                <span class="qual-text"><strong>Business with consolidated operation.</strong> You already sell, have clients, but the process is manual and depends on you for everything</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="qual-icon"><i data-lucide="check" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
                <span class="qual-text"><strong>Revenue from R$ 100k/month.</strong> Investment is recovered within the first 60-90 days of catalyzed operation</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="qual-icon"><i data-lucide="check" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
                <span class="qual-text"><strong>Willingness to transform.</strong> You want to change how the business operates, not just add a tool</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="qual-col no">
            <div class="qual-header"><span class="qual-badge">It’s not for you</span></div>
            <ul class="qual-list">
              <li>
                <span class="qual-icon"><i data-lucide="x" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
                <span class="qual-text"><strong>Business in validation phase.</strong> If you are still testing the model, Opera OS is not a priority now</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="qual-icon"><i data-lucide="x" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
                <span class="qual-text"><strong>Expectation of immediate results.</strong> Real transformation takes 10-12 weeks. If you need 2 weeks, we are not the option</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="qual-icon"><i data-lucide="x" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
                <span class="qual-text"><strong>Resistance to process change.</strong> Opera OS changes how the business operates. Those unwilling to change should not hire</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="qual-icon"><i data-lucide="x" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
                <span class="qual-text"><strong>Looking for a quick fix.</strong> If the problem is only the website or only WhatsApp, we have smaller solutions</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PRICING -->
    <section id="investimento" aria-labelledby="pricing-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header reveal" style="text-align:center; align-items:center;">
          <p class="eyebrow" style="justify-content:center;">Investment</p>
          <h2 id="pricing-heading">An investment <em>for growth</em>.</h2>
          <p style="margin: 0 auto;">OperaOS is a tailored investment, defined after diagnosis and before any commitment. Each business has different gaps. We present the exact value in the proposal, no fine print, no surprise add-ons.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pricing-grid reveal">
          <div class="pricing-card featured">
            <span class="pricing-badge">Start here</span>
            <h3 class="pricing-name">Opera OS</h3>
            <div class="pricing-price" style="font-size: 2.2rem;">Tailored</div>
            <p class="pricing-period">defined in diagnosis</p>
            <ul class="pricing-features">
              <li>All 5 phases of the OPERA method</li>
              <li>CRM integrated with agents</li>
              <li>AI agents trained on your business</li>
              <li>Website and sales pages</li>
              <li>Complete automations</li>
              <li>Configured and integrated support hub</li>
              <li>Team training</li>
              <li>Support throughout implementation</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/en/contato" class="btn btn-primary" style="width:100%; justify-content:center;" id="pricing-cta-primary">
              Schedule free diagnosis <span class="btn-arrow">→</span>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="pricing-card secondary">
            <span class="pricing-badge">Continuity</span>
            <h3 class="pricing-name">Evolution Retainer</h3>
            <div class="pricing-price" style="font-size: 2.2rem;">Upon request</div>
            <p class="pricing-period">after Opera OS delivery</p>
            <ul class="pricing-features">
              <li>Continuous maintenance and monitoring</li>
              <li>AI agent optimization</li>
              <li>New flows and automations</li>
              <li>Monthly performance reports</li>
              <li>Consultative support</li>
              <li>Matika license included</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/en/contato" class="btn btn-secondary" style="width:100%; justify-content:center;" id="pricing-cta-retainer">
              Learn more
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- COMO COMEÇAR -->
    <section id="como-comecar" aria-labelledby="comecar-heading">
      <div class="container container-sm">
        <div class="section-header reveal">
          <p class="eyebrow">How to Start</p>
          <h2 id="comecar-heading">Four steps until the system <em>is running</em>.</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline reveal">
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-dot">01</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h3>Contact</h3>
              <p>Fill out the form or contact via WhatsApp. Our team will reach out within 24 hours to qualify and schedule.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-dot">02</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h3>Diagnosis</h3>
              <p>45-minute session where we deeply understand your operation. Free for qualified profiles.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-dot">03</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h3>Proposal</h3>
              <p>We present the complete Opera OS plan with scope, timeline, KPIs, and investment defined for your reality.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-dot">04</div>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <h3>Implementation</h3>
               <p>Contract signed, Phase O starts the following week. In 10 to 12 weeks, the system is running.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal" style="text-align:center; margin-top: 48px;">
          <div class="cta-buttons">
            <a href="/en/contato" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" id="comecar-cta">
              Schedule free diagnosis <span class="btn-arrow">→</span>
            </a>
            <a href="https://wa.me/5575991879786?text=Hello!%20I%20would%20like%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20Catalise.me's%20Opera%20OS." target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg" id="comecar-whatsapp">
              Chat on WhatsApp
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section id="faq" aria-labelledby="faq-heading">
      <div class="container container-sm">
        <div class="section-header reveal">
          <p class="eyebrow">FAQ</p>
          <h2 id="faq-heading">Frequently asked <em>questions</em>.</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-list reveal">
          <div class="faq-item" id="faq-1">
            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-1">
              <span class="faq-question-text">What type of business does Opera OS work for?</span>
              <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-answer-1" role="region">
              <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                <p>It was designed for service businesses: hospitality, clinics, driving schools, real estate, education, legal, and other segments where support, sales funnel, and operations are the main bottlenecks. If you sell services and have a consolidated operation, Opera OS adapts to your context.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item" id="faq-2">
            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-2">
              <span class="faq-question-text">Do I need a technical team to operate?</span>
              <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-answer-2" role="region">
              <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                <p>No. All onboarding is done by Catalise.me. The team receives practical training on using each system, and all documentation is delivered in operational, not technical, language. You don’t need IT to use Opera OS.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item" id="faq-3">
            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-3">
              <span class="faq-question-text">What happens after implementation?</span>
              <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-answer-3" role="region">
              <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                <p>Opera OS is delivered functioning and documented. You can operate independently. For clients who want continuous evolution: new agents, new automations, system optimization, monthly reports, we offer the Evolution Retainer upon request.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item" id="faq-4">
            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-4">
              <span class="faq-question-text">What is the investment?</span>
              <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-answer-4" role="region">
              <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                <p>For companies with revenue from R$ 100k/month. Investment proportional to operation, defined in diagnosis. Final scope is defined in Phase O because each business has different gaps. Final value is fixed at plan presentation before any financial commitment.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA FINAL -->
    <section class="cta-section" aria-labelledby="opera-cta-heading">
      <div class="container" style="position: relative; z-index: 1;">
        <p class="eyebrow" style="justify-content: center;">Next step</p>
        <h2 id="opera-cta-heading">Start with <em>free diagnosis</em>.</h2>
        <p>In 45 minutes, we’ll help identify operational bottlenecks, estimated financial impacts, and design a personalized implementation plan for your context.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/en/contato" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" id="opera-final-cta">
            Schedule free diagnosis <span class="btn-arrow">→</span>
          </a>
          <a href="https://wa.me/5575991879786" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg" id="opera-final-whatsapp">
            Chat on WhatsApp
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

</BaseLayout>
